    "In financial QA, models answer questions about company disclosures, regulatory text, or market data.",
    "For example, a user may ask, \"What was Company X's net income last quarter?\"",
    "or \"Under which clause must this fund disclose assets?\"",
    "These tasks can be open-book (access to filings or transcripts) or closed-book (testing",
